## Technical Architecture

### Advanced Control Integration

- **Phase-Locked Loop (PLL):** Vertex synchronization, prevents resonance
- **Model-Predictive Control (MPC):** Real-time ramp optimization
- **Fault-Tolerant Re-sequencing:** Automatic recovery protocols
- **Integrated VAR Management:** Propulsion/power factor dual control

### Safety & Regulatory Framework

- **Defense in Depth:** Physics-based → Passive → Active safety layers
- **Staged Licensing:** Magnetic commissioning → Nuclear operation permits
- **Emergency Protocols:** <90 second recovery to safe state from any failure
- **Marine Standards:** Compatible with international waters flagging

